You are given a string s. You need to reverse the string.

Example 1:

Input:
s = Geeks
Output: skeeG
Example 2:

Input:
s = for
Output: rof

----------------------

class Reverse
{
    // Complete the function
    // str: input string
    public static String reverseWord(String str)
    {
        // Reverse the string str
       String res="";
        
      for(int i=str.length()-1;i>=0;i--){
          res+=str.charAt(i);
      }
        return res;
    }
}
